Paper: hep-th/0210237

Date: 2002-10-24

Title: Yang-Mills and Born-Infeld actions on finite group spaces

Authors: P.Aschieri, L.Castellani, A.P.Isaev

Comments: Talk presented at GROUP24, Paris, July 2002. LaTeX, 4 pages, IOP

stylesDiscretized nonabelian gauge theories living on finite group spaces G aredefined by means of a geometric action \int Tr F\wedge *F . This technique isextended to obtain a discrete version of the Born-Infeld action.